iations">Authors and Affiliations</h3><ol class="c-article-author-affiliation__list"><li id="Aff1"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Biological Sciences, Middle East Technical University, Ankara, Turkey</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Erinç Yurtman, Onur Özer, Eren Yüncü, Nihan Dilşad Dağtaş, Mustafa Özkan, Damla Kaptan, Gözde Atağ, Kıvılcım Başak Vural, Gülşah Merve Kılınç, Ayshin Ghalichi, Sinan Can Açan, Reyhan Yaka, Ekin Sağlıcan, C. Can Bilgin, Sevgi Yorulmaz, Mehmet Somel &amp; İnci Togan</p></li><li id="Aff2"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Emmy Noether Group Evolutionary Immunogenomics, Max Planck Institute for Evolutionary Biology, Plön, Germany</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Onur Özer</p></li><li id="Aff3"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Health Informatics, Middle East Technical University, Ankara, Turkey</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Dilek Koptekin</p></li><li id="Aff4"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Prehistory, Istanbul University, Laleli, Istanbul, Turkey</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Yasin Gökhan Çakan &amp; Erhan Bıçakçı</p></li><li id="Aff5"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Anthropology, Ankara University, Ankara, Turkey</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Ali Akbaba</p></li><li id="Aff6"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Archaeology, Batman University, Batman, Turkey</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Can Yümni Gündem</p></li><li id="Aff7"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Institute of Archaeology, University College London, London, UK</p><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__authors-list">Louise Martin</p></li><li id="Aff8"><p class="c-article-author-affiliation__address">Department of Bioinformatics, Graduate School of H